headline: Huntington Bancshares Incorporated Decreases Its Prime Rate To 7 Percent
summary: Huntington Bancshares Incorporated (Nasdaq: HBAN) announced that its prime rate is decreasing from 7.25 percent to 7.00 percent, effective October 30, 2025.
